<lb ed="T" n="0322c07"/><head><persName key="A000883">攝摩騰</persName>一</head>
<p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0322c15"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0322c15"/><persName key="A000883">攝摩騰</persName>，本<placeName key="PL000000048208">中天竺</placeName>人，善風儀，解大小乘經，
<lb ed="T" n="0322c16"/>常遊化為任。昔經往<placeName key="PL000000048207">天竺</placeName>附庸小國講《金
<lb ed="T" n="0322c17"/>光明經》，會敵國侵境，<persName key="A000883">騰</persName>惟曰：「經云：『能說此<ptr target="fn15"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0322c18"/>經法。為地神所護。使所居安樂。』今鋒鏑
<lb ed="T" n="0322c19"/>方始，曾是為益乎！」乃誓以忘身，躬往和勸，
<lb ed="T" n="0322c20"/>遂二國交歡，由是<ptr target="fn16"/>顯<ptr target="fn17"/>達。</p><p><date from-iso="+0060-03-04" key="j17430381746670" to-iso="+0070-02-12">漢永平中</date>，<persName key="A002001">明皇帝</persName>
<lb ed="T" n="0322c21"/>夜夢金人<ptr target="fn18"/>飛空而至，乃大集群臣，以占所
<lb ed="T" n="0322c22"/>夢。通人<persName key="A002002">傅毅</persName>奉答：「<ref type="person" target="#A002002">臣</ref>聞<placeName key="PL000000047439">西域</placeName>有神，其名曰
<lb ed="T" n="0322c23"/>『 佛』。<ref type="person" target="#A002001">陛下</ref>所夢將必是乎。」<ref type="person" target="#A002001">帝</ref>以為然，即遣郎
<lb ed="T" n="0322c24"/>中<persName key="A002003">蔡愔</persName>、博士弟子<persName key="A002004">秦景</persName>等。使往<placeName key="PL000000048207">天竺</placeName>，尋訪
<lb ed="T" n="0322c25"/>佛法。<persName key="A002003">愔</persName>等於彼遇見<persName key="A000883">摩騰</persName>，乃要還<placeName key="PL000000000098">漢地</placeName>。<persName key="A000883">騰</persName>
<lb ed="T" n="0322c26"/>誓志弘通，不憚疲苦，冒涉流沙，至乎<placeName key="PL000000023521">雒
<lb ed="T" n="0322c27"/>邑</placeName>，<persName key="A002001">明帝</persName>甚加賞接，於城西門外立精舍以
<lb ed="T" n="0322c28"/>處之，<placeName key="PL000000000098">漢</placeName>地有沙門之始也。但大法初傳，未
<lb ed="T" n="0322c29"/>有歸信，故蘊其深解，無所宣述。後少時
<lb ed="T" n="0323a01"/>卒於<placeName key="PL000000023521">雒陽</placeName>。有記云：<persName key="A000883">騰</persName>譯《四十二章經》一卷。
<lb ed="T" n="0323a02"/>初緘在<placeName key="PL000000058486">蘭臺</placeName>石室第十四間中。<persName key="A000883">騰</persName>所住處，今
<lb ed="T" n="0323a03"/><placeName key="PL000000023521">雒陽</placeName>城西<placeName key="PL000000023533">雍門</placeName>外<placeName key="PL000000023663">白馬寺</placeName>是也。相傳云：外國
<lb ed="T" n="0323a04"/>國王嘗毀破諸寺，唯<placeName key="PL000000023663">招提寺</placeName>未及毀壞。夜
<lb ed="T" n="0323a05"/>有一白馬繞塔悲鳴，即以啟王，王即停壞
<lb ed="T" n="0323a06"/>諸寺。因改<placeName key="PL000000023663">招提</placeName>以為「<placeName key="PL000000023663">白馬</placeName>」。故諸寺立名多
<lb ed="T" n="0323a07"/>取則焉。</p>

